2025-04-16.description:

2025-06-13.title: York VS BIMM (Test Match)
2025-06-13.description:
A 6v6 Test Match between York and BIMM. This will serve as a test of the Cheep Cheep app and YouTube streaming. Members of the relevant teams can sign up to compete in this match using the button in the team's announcement channel.

This match will be streamed on the UMKL YouTube channel. You can visit it here: https://www.youtube.com/@universitymariokartleague.
